text:
Please, guys, let's make a Naya Nepal.
Naya Nepal means 
1. No Caste System exists in our society
2. Rhino as the national animal of Nepal
3. English as the official language of Nepal
4. Maintain a close relationship with China but distance away from India
5. Open Border with China
6. Replace Indian Brahmins with Kirati priest at the Pashupatinath temple 
7. Change the name of Mt. Everest with our own local name  Chomolungma
8. Stop showing Indian movies in Nepal
9. Woman ministers should not wear saree but should wear our ethnic costume
10. The Prime Minister of Nepal needs to have at least a bachelor degree from a University 


the list goes on.....
So guys stop discriminating people who do lowly jobs such as sweeping the streets, cutting the meat, cleaning the toilets and public places. Instead, appreciate them because, without those people who do lowly jobs, it becomes an unbearable place to live in.
Together we can create Naya Nepal, New Nepal.
